body_html: All of the content on tensorflow.org (without the fancy styling and some math formatting) is also available on github, in the tensorflow/g3doc folder. The HTML on tensorflow.org is generated quite similarly to what github's MarkDown viewer does, so the experience shouldn't be all that different.
